Class Tuple<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.google.calendar.interoperability.connectorplugin.base.Tuple<T>

public class Tuple<T>
extends Object

A pair of two elements of the same kind. This is a very simple container -- it does not do toString, comparison or hashcode correctly. Do not use it as key in collections.
